{"tid":2400831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣開放境外學生透過專案申請入境 入境後需隔離16日","createTime":"2021-02-09T09:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:55:12.000Z","uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"09ece4ab3a6847b98a64b5aa99cdd0c6c89c4ca9","tid":2400831,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"經過一個多月的等待，教育部於2月8日晚間發函給各校，宣布即日起受理境外生入境申請，含所有學位生及先修華語的外交部台灣獎學金受獎生，<br />\n<br />\n境外生要先跟所屬學校討論好入境事宜，由學校到「境外生來台就學資訊系統」填寫相關表格。教育部表示，考量名冊核定及公文送發所需時間，學校需於5個工作日前上傳（以名冊內最早班機為準）。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102090178.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102090178.aspx&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNME6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=fd7ad61a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102090178.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"0a176d1265ee39ba830236e1322d28d3bb2bb13f","tid":2400831,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"14+2隔離"},{"pid":"8aa4e3a8323b9f1c5a370fde6a227b0226f1c302","tid":2400831,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e53e35597b1e1b0bab730035fe9c01cf6153cc","tid":2400831,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa4e3a8323b9f1c5a370fde6a227b0226f1c302","tid":2400831,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youar